quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,100,"∆Āeen adinoo…ďe [gooŇč…óinal] adii…ďe e fer…ďe …ďeen e weernu…ďe wallitii…ďe …ďeen, e …ďen jokku…ďe e …ďeen no mo∆ī∆īiri, Alla welaama …ďe, kam…ďe kadi …ďe mbelaama mo. o maranii …ďe Aljannaaji …ói caatli ilata ley majji, ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe ton poomaa. Ko …óuum woni malal mawnungal."
  9,101,"Hino e …ďeen won …ďe banŇče mon jeyaa…ďe e yim…ďe ladde …ďen,naafigee…ďe,e yim…ďe Madiina …ďeen kadi.…ďe candol…óinii e naafigaagu.A anndaa …ďe, minen mi…óen nganndi …ďe.Aray min lepta …ďe laabi …ói…ói,refti …ďe nduttitee e lepte mawnu…óe."
  9,102,"E wo…ó…ďe goo, kirlii…ďe bakkatuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďe njilli gollal mo∆ī∆īal e go…óngal bon gal. Hino tijja nde Alla ja…ďanta …ďe tuubuubuyee.Pellet, Alla ko jaafooo…óo, jurmotoo…óo."
  9,103,"∆≥ettu e jaw…óeele ma…ď…ďe …óen sadaka, la…ď…ďiniraa…ďe lootiraa…ďe mo, ndu'ano…óaa …ďe. Pellet, du'aa maa ko dee∆īere wonan de …ďe. Alla ko Nanoowo, ganndu…óo."
  9,104,"E …ďe ngannda won de ko Alla no ja…ďana jeyaa…ďe makko …ďen tuubuubuyee, himo ja…ďa sadakaaji …óin, e won de ko Alla woni Ja…ďoowo tuubuubuyee, ko jurmotoo…óo."
  9,105,"Maaku : "ngollee, arma Alla yi'a golle mon …óeen, e nulaa…óo makko on e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen. Aray ruttita-…óon ka ganndu…óo ko wirni eko fee√Īi …óin, O humpita on ko ngollayno…óon"."
  9,106,"E wo…ó…ďe goo ko nennanaa…ďe e yamiroore Alla : immaa O lepta …ďe, maa O ja…ďana …ďe tuubuubuyee. Alla ko ganndu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo."